column2:
combine_data$type = as.factor(combine_data$type)
levels(combine_data$type) = c('CN-LOH','AMP','DEL',"Undetermined")
ggplot(subset(combine_data,type %in% c('CN-LOH','AMP','DEL')), aes(x=type, y=cf, fill=type)) + 
  theme_classic() +
  geom_boxplot() + 
  ylab('Cell Fraction') + 
  geom_jitter(position=position_jitter(width=0.3, height=0.2),aes(colour=type), alpha=0.7) +
  ggtitle("Cell Fractions vs. detected CNAs")
dev.off()
